plate, and thus has a vast legacy to live up to. Thanks to these highly detailed spy shots, we can all rest assured knowing that, at the very least, the VW ID.2 GTI won’t be so bloated. With its smartly compact proportions and short wheelbase, it’s safe to say that this electric GTI will be a blast to throw around tight corners–a true staple of any authentic GTI. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"VW ID.2 GTI Spy Shot\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzQ1/vw-id2-gti-12.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"do-fully-electric-and-hot-hatch-really-belong-in-the-same-sentence\"\u003eDo “fully-electric” and “hot hatch” really belong in the same sentence?\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eAs a hard-headed purist myself, there’s no denying that the idea of a fully-electric hot hatch is ample grounds for skepticism. However, thanks to the precedent set by the lauded \u003ca href=\"https://www.autoblog.com/hyundai/\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003eHyundai\u003c/a\u003e Ioniq 5 N, which proved that a driver-focused electric hatchback really could put a smile on your face, my hopes are high for Volkswagen’s entry into this new and exciting segment. I’ll admit that I wish VW’s integration of electric hot hatches into its lineup didn’t mean its gas-powered sports models will likely be phased out entirely, but it’s at least somewhat comforting to know that we won’t be left entirely without that necessary “fun factor” that made hot hatches so appealing in the first place. \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Volkswagen ID.2 GTI Concept\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1456\" height=\"816\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE2NzMx/coleattisha_63292_httpss-mj-runaz-gmycu6te_2025_volkswagen_el_b1566b7b-d15a-400b-8ab1-0f9ce1a3d79e_0-916731.png\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts-the-vw-id-2-gti-carries-a-massive-weight-on-its-shoulders\"\u003eFinal thoughts: The VW ID.2 GTI carries a massive weight on its shoulders\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eAs the VW ID.2 GTI will be the German automaker’s first-ever fully-electric performance model, its critical reception will truly be a “make or break” moment for the brand. If the model excites and demonstrates a genuinely well-executed effort, it could cement VW as a serious heavy-hitter in the segment, as it has been for so many years with models such as the Golf GTI and Polo GTI. On the other hand, if it lacks the passion and vibrance that buyers have come to expect from driver-oriented cars, it could cost VW a lot of the hype they’ll need to maintain for the inevitable release of the e-Golf GTI. Until we see more from Volkswagen, we remain hopeful and optimistic that the brand’s engineers will be able to translate their traditional hot hatch passion into a progressive and forward-thinking EV.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eAbout the Author\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"100px\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 1200w, htt